  "text": "Email from The Walletwise Hospitality LLC Profitable for Owner-Operator Opportunity (3\u00d7 Revenue) \u200a Sunbelt Lodge Abbeville, Louisiana Price: $1,550,000 | 100 Rooms Exceptional High-Return Investment (2.8\u00d7 Revenue) Click Here To Access Data Room \u200a \u200a Exceptional Investment Opportunity An outstanding investment and owner-operator opportunity is now available in the thriving community of Abbeville, Louisiana. Property Highlights Prime Location & Visibility: High-traffic Veterans Memorial Drive frontage ensures excellent visibility. Close to local dining, retail, and major roadways connecting to Lafayette and the Gulf Coast. Strong Operating Base: Currently averaging 35\u201340 weekly guests with no reliance on online booking platforms. Consistent repeat clientele provides stable, year-round cash flow. Growth & Upside Potential: Significant opportunity to boost revenue by adding online booking channels (Booking.com, Expedia, Airbnb). Ideal for expanding corporate contracts, travel nurse housing, or oilfield service lodging. Property Features: Well-maintained lodge with spacious parking, easy drive-up access, and clean, functional guest rooms. Flexible floor plan and management options to suit different operating models. Investment Benefits Immediate income from established weekly guest base. Owner-friendly operations with manageable staffing needs. Opportunity to increase occupancy and daily rates with minimal capital improvements. This property is perfect for investors, hospitality professionals, or family operators seeking a profitable business with room to grow. View All Our Listings \u200a Pratik Patel 945-268-4828 info@thewalletwise.com  www.thewalletwise.com  Call Pratik Dipika Patel 214-291-6293 info@thewalletwise.com  www.thewalletwise.com  Call Dipika \u200a The Walletwise Hospitality \ufeff Specializing in buying and selling hotels across the U.S., we connect owners with qualified buyers to maximize value and ensure smooth transactions. With market expertise and a strong industry network, we are your trusted partner in hospitality real estate.     The Walletwise Hospitality LLC | Hickory Chase Ln | Melissa , TX 75454 US Unsubscribe | Update Profile | Constant Contact Data Notice \u200a",
